&lt;p&gt;Adprime is the largest digital Healthcare publishing platform and programmatic provider that offers solutions for reaching healthcare professionals (HCP) and direct-to-consumer (DTC) brands.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Adprime is seeking a results-driven Sales Executive with experience in the hospital and healthcare sector to drive revenue growth by calling on healthcare agencies and direct client accounts. The ideal candidate has a strong background in digital advertising, with hands-on experience managing and selling display and programmatic campaigns. This role requires a consultative sales approach, strong relationship-building skills, and the ability to translate client needs into effective advertising solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
