&lt;li&gt;Develop and manage relationships with healthcare agencies and direct healthcare/hospital clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, pursue, and close new business opportunities within the healthcare and hospital market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sell and manage digital advertising solutions, with a focus on display and programmatic campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with internal campaign management and operations teams to ensure successful campaign execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate clients on campaign strategy, targeting, performance metrics, and optimization opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and deliver sales presentations, proposals, and media plans tailored to healthcare clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor campaign performance and provide insights, reporting, and recommendations to clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate pipeline and account activity tracking in CRM systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on healthcare industry trends, regulations, and digital advertising best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
